{"type": "article", "id": 3462, "title": "北极熊杯盖", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-12T07:23:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232827f7oZIGHuWBYzA3kC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本设计工作室 Necktie 日前带来了一款北极熊造型的陶瓷杯盖，名为「Shirokuma 」。请注意，这只颜色雪白、造型可爱的北极熊可不只是满足装饰作用，它坐在杯盖上，手里拿着一根钓竿，可以帮助喝茶的用户提住茶包线，避免它落入茶杯内，此外，杯盖上还可以放置一些小零食。Shirokuma 直径为 11 厘米，可适用于一般的马克杯或者玻璃杯，定价 3000 日元，<a href=\"http://necktie.onlinestores.jp/category/select/pid/8765\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232824hQ4X2fNZxJPqUncu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232825N9ATDm3tjBYMzSyQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232825MUth0OKEfH2j3n8k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232826HPivhGW7wpcUqdsK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232826ufoNVz9RvE18tbaX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}